title: An Asymmetry: "Pro-Capitalism" vs. "Pro-Communism".
description: A follow-up video on many (many!) in which I've more directly dealt with mass-murder and (man-made) mass-starvation under Communist regimes (thus, you may notice, those themes and issues are not discussed here).  I also mention an earlier video with Capitalism in the title that replies to a very memorable email I received from a Mapuche man from Argentina, and you can find that here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CZpcyJmKGoc
